Asylum and refugee casework, ESOL and integration support is documentation-heavy with interpreter scheduling.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
Community charities often run on CRM-lite tools plus spreadsheets. AI training and virtual assistance for coordination frequently land well when tied to visible admin pain.

