  ('ea0f679f-e6e4-5f44-b3d7-48959f98fd3b', 'THE PROSPECTS TRUST', 'Charity', 'REACH, CAMBRIDGESHIRE, CB25 0HZ, Cambridgeshire', 'Cambridgeshire', 'https://www.prospectstrust.org.uk', 12, 979123, 'FY ending 2025-03-31; Charity Commission latest income', 3, 'The Prospects Trust is all about the people who come through the gates, and our gates are always open. We provide meaningful work experience sessions on an 18 acre organically certified farm near Reach, Cambridge for adults with learning difficulties, physical disabilities and mental ill health.', 'Medium', '2026-06-24', 'primary', '', 'Chief Executive', 'enquiries@prospectstrust.org.uk', '01638741551', 'https://register-of-charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/en/charity-search/-/charity-details/1048584/full-print', 'https://www.prospectstrust.org.uk', ARRAY['health'], ARRAY['health'], 'MEETING PREP — THE PROSPECTS TRUST (Health & wellbeing)

WHAT THE ORGANISATION DOES:
The Prospects Trust is all about the people who come through the gates, and our gates are always open. We provide meaningful work experience sessions on an 18 acre organically certified farm near Reach, Cambridge for adults with learning difficulties, physical disabilities and mental ill health.

ORGANISATION CONTEXT:
REACH, CAMBRIDGESHIRE, CB25 0HZ, Cambridgeshire, Cambridgeshire. ~12 staff; income on record £979,123.

RECOMMENDED VAxAI ENTRY: Training + policy guidance

WHY ADMIN / AI PRESSURE IS HIGH:
Health and wellbeing delivery needs appointment coordination, clinical liaison and case records.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
