WHAT THE ORGANISATION DOES:
The Trustees operate a general grant giving policy, providing funds for such individuals or charitable objects or institution as the Trustees think fit, within the UK. The Charity''s objects are to enable participation in art''s based education and training, to fund visual and creative arts programmes, and to help prepare entry for individuals to an art''s based occupation or career.

